    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（けれども突如、日本の第一線を離れてアメリカに移住）",
      "startTime": 9.2020862262,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk002.wav",
      "text": "（以降、ライブバトルには何年も参加していない）",
      "startTime": 14.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（にも関わらず、圧倒的な累積スコアで君臨し二位の）",
      "startTime": 18.5995695432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk003.wav",
      "text": "（Baroqueもとうとう記録を抜けないままに引退）",
      "startTime": 23.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 27.2670304299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あ……ヨーコさんがいるということは",
      "startTime": 27.2670304299,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk004.wav",
      "text": "NexusFesに出演する日本のアイドルって……",
      "startTime": 31.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 34.464966933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle001.wav",
      "text": "そうよ、彼女も出演予定なの",
      "startTime": 34.464966933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "日本から、あなたの今のグループも出るとは聞いてるわ",
      "startTime": 37.8982987404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle002.wav",
      "text": "今日はそのための、敵情視察ってとこかしら？",
      "startTime": 42.5895012855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.9316305478
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……なんてね、冗談よ。ここはアメリカだもの",
      "startTime": 46.9316305478,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle003.wav",
      "text": "VENUSプログラムはないんだから、安心して",
      "startTime": 51.3895012855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "彼女が渡米したのは存じてましたが……",
      "startTime": 54.6982974688,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk005.wav",
      "text": "ヨーコさんまで一緒だったんですね",
      "startTime": 57.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 60.2712454159
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "歌って踊る以外、何も覚える気がない子なんだもの",
      "startTime": 60.2712454159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle004.wav",
      "text": "誰かが面倒見なきゃ、すぐに野垂れ死んじゃうわ",
      "startTime": 64.6769161541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それに……「みんなを幸せにしたい」って言ってた子を",
      "startTime": 68.5045797665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle005.wav",
      "text": "こんな業界に引っ張り込んだ、その責任は取らないとね",
      "startTime": 74.1102494875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 78.17124389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk006.wav",
      "text": "あの頃……渡米前に、一体彼女に何があったんですか？",
      "startTime": 78.17124389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 84.4223992346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "日本にいる頃は、一位、一位と随分持てはやされて",
      "startTime": 84.4223992346,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle006.wav",
      "text": "最初は嬉しそうだったんだけど、だんだん参ってきてね",
      "startTime": 89.7758717535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "自分に負けて、ステージ裏で泣いてる子を見るのが辛い",
      "startTime": 94.3557295161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle007.wav",
      "text": "私は誰かを泣かせるために歌ってる訳じゃない、って",
      "startTime": 99.1092050868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 103.3224022864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すみません、私は華やかな姿しか知らなかったので",
      "startTime": 103.3224022864,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk007.wav",
      "text": "そんなこととは思わず……",
      "startTime": 108.4666651408,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "隠してたもの、当然よ。……まぁ今は、アメリカに来て",
      "startTime": 110.4632642427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle008.wav",
      "text": "普通のステージに出る分には、楽しそうにしてるわ",
      "startTime": 116.3574580213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 119.9632601737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さて、あなたはそろそろ楽屋に戻った方がいいわよ",
      "startTime": 119.9632601737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle009.wav",
      "text": "本番前の準備が始まる頃合いだから",
      "startTime": 124.5645339646,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 127.6632642427
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それと……藤代さんのことは、残念だったわね",
      "startTime": 127.6632642427,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle010.wav",
      "text": "Sundanceは、本当にいいアイドルだったのに",
      "startTime": 133.4978672979,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いえ……そう言っていただけるだけで",
      "startTime": 137.1299207369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-mhk008.wav",
      "text": "葉ちゃんも私も、救われます",
      "startTime": 140.8333297729,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vancorridor-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "vancorridor-00-night",
      "startTime": 143.2611229259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ⅢXのステージを、楽しみに観させてもらうわ",
      "startTime": 143.2611229259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "ヨーコ・ボイル",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-yokboyle011.wav",
      "text": "あなたのグループだもの、きっと素敵なんでしょうね",
      "startTime": 147.1768677072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.0111168224
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ん？　まだkana達が袖にいるのに、映像が始まった",
      "startTime": 153.0611168224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.5068469454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-kan001.wav",
      "text": "あー、ステージ前にkana達の紹介入れてるのか",
      "startTime": 158.5068469454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.6799832343
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私達、日本じゃ最初から知名度あったし",
      "startTime": 162.6799832343,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2507_01_04-kor001.wav",
      "text": "いちいち紹介してもらわなくても良かったものねぇ",
      "startTime": 166.4768677072,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.146649901
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私がパリコレ出た時の……miho、随分若いじゃない",
      "startTime": 170.146649901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 174.143183028
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
